```python
def fib4(n: int) -> int:
    fibs = [0, 0, 2, 0]
    for i in range(4, n + 1):
        fibs.append(fibs[i - 1] + fibs[i - 2] + fibs[i - 3] + fibs[i - 4])
    return fibs[n]
```
